      "text": "All LibraVox recordings are in the public domain.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 6.12,
      "end": 11.16,
      "text": "For more information, or to volunteer, please visit LibraVox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 11.8,
      "end": 15.78,
      "text": "Recorded by Christine Doer, the known as Assa, Florida.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 17.54,
      "end": 20.92,
      "text": "Esaups Fables, the boy, and the filberts.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 21.42,
      "end": 26.72,
      "text": "A boy put his hand into a jar of filberts, and grasped as many as his fist could possibly",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 26.72,
      "end": 27.12,
      "text": "hold.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 27.12,
      "end": 31.58,
      "text": "But when he tried to pull it out again, he found he couldn't do so.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 32.34,
      "end": 36.82,
      "text": "For the neck of the jar was too small to allow the passage of so large a handful.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 38.04,
      "end": 43.78,
      "text": "Unwilling to lose his nuts, but unable to withdraw his hand, he burst into tears.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 44.94,
      "end": 47.96,
      "text": "A bystander who saw where the trouble lay said to him,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 48.66,
      "end": 51.08,
      "text": "Come, my boy, don't be so greedy.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 51.7,
      "end": 56.78,
      "text": "Be content with half the amount, and you'll be able to get your hand out without difficulty.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 58.2,
      "end": 60.74,
      "text": "Do not attempt too much at once.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-014",
      "start": 62.48,
      "end": 65.24,
      "text": "End of the boy and the filberts.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
